(40, 21, 32, 40, 21, 25, 25, 'believed him not', 'Connection of Belief in John', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of belief in John the Baptist. In Matthew 21:25, the question of John''s authority highlights the failure to believe, which is echoed in Matthew 21:32 where the publicans and harlots believed him while others did not.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
