(40, 21, 33, 22, 8, 11, 12, 'let it out to husbandmen', 'Vineyard Ownership and Stewardship', 'This connection highlights the theme of vineyard ownership and stewardship in both passages. The householder in Matthew and Solomon in Song of Solomon both entrust their vineyards to keepers, emphasizing the responsibility of caretaking for what belongs to them.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
