(40, 21, 33, 39, 2, 4, 9, NULL, 'Covenant and Stewardship Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the responsibility of caretakers in a covenant relationship. The householder in Matthew entrusts the vineyard to husbandmen, paralleling the covenant with Levi in Malachi, where priests are expected to uphold the law and guide the people.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
