(40, 21, 34, 23, 5, 4, 4, 'the fruits of it', 'Vineyard and Fruit Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the expectation of fruit from a vineyard. In Matthew, the servants are sent to receive the fruits, while Isaiah questions why the vineyard produced wild grapes instead of expected fruit.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
