(40, 22, 30, 40, 24, 38, 38, NULL, 'Marriage and the End Times', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of marrying and giving in marriage. Matthew 22:30 discusses the absence of marriage in the resurrection, while Matthew 24:38 highlights the prevalence of marriage before the flood, suggesting a contrast between earthly life and heavenly existence.', 'theme', 0.307, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
